data.description: Welcome to 741 Oak Manor Drive in Marengo, Illinois, a Tudor-style gem, nestled in an established neighborhood. This inviting four-bedroom home offers two full and two half-baths, blending traditional elegance with the needs of modern living.    Upon entry, the dramatic two-story foyer with its striking beamed ceiling sets a welcoming tone. A flexible room adjacent to the entryway can serve as an efficient office space or a formal dining room, adapting effortlessly to your lifestyle needs.    For those seeking a quiet retreat, the loft sitting room is a perfect hideaway for reading and relaxation. Car enthusiasts will appreciate the heated garage's extended area for tool storage and projects. The versatile Shed Mahal in the backyard provides additional space for storage or hobbies within the privacy of a fenced-in yard.    The heart of the home features a functional kitchen that caters to everyday living, while the basement's bonus family room and half bath offer extra space for leisure and entertainment.    Located with easy access to I-90, this home combines the tranquility of suburban living with the convenience of city connectivity. 741 Oak Manor Drive is an ideal setting for those looking to enjoy the best of both worlds.
